omial size, where $\\text{EMAJ}$\nis the \"exact majority\" function, improving previous lower bounds against\n$\\text{ACC}^0$ [Williams JACM'14] and $\\text{ACC}^0 \\circ \\text{THR}$ [Williams\nSTOC'14], [Murray-Williams STOC'18]. This is the first nontrivial lower bound\nagainst such a circuit class.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2020 21:49:02 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-01-23"}
