g range without substantially\nincreasing device volume or energy consumption, making it desirable for a wide\nrange of imaging and display applications.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 21 Jan 2020 22:31:42 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 23 Jan 2020 23:05:05 GMT"},{"version":"v3","created":"Sat, 21 Nov 2020 17:33:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-11-24"}
