h the\nprevious notion, that recovers the results of Harris and Omar for $b\\in\n\\mathbb{Q}^{*}$ in $2$-dimensions; and show that the proportion of\n$\\bf{b}$-visible points in this case only depends on the negative entries of\n$\\bf{b}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 22 Jan 2020 00:22:20 GMT"}],"update_date":"2021-03-10"}
